   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Ba, singur te voi nfrunta, Hagen, aa ct te crezi tu de nebiruit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/>nzuat i narmat, Iring porni cu pas hotrt ctre burgunzi. Hagen iei</text:p>
